<p>3.Greer, F.R., et al., Pediatrics 143 e20190281 (2019).</p>
<p>4.Jantscher-Krenn, E. &amp; Bode, L., Minerva Pediatr 64 83-99 (2012).</p>
<p>5.Jantscher-Krenn, E. et al., Gut 61 1417-1425 (2011).</p>
<p>6.Yu, Z.T., et al., J Nutr 146 1980-1990 (2016).</p>
